snippet.textDisplay:
Now I want chocolate cookies soooo baaaaad! 🤤

I just learned the other day that there's a thing called black cocoa powder. if you use that instead lf regular cocoa powder I bet they'll taste even more like oreos!

Also, helpful tip for putting icing in piping bags (even though I'm sure your aries self won't listen lol)...put your bag in a tall glass and fold the bag over the glass edge. Then you can easily scoop your filling in and the glass will hold it up for you and you won't get all that mess all over the top of the bag lol...and you don't really need a piping tip for something like this, that's just more mess to clean...just put it in the bag and snip the tip off 👍🏻

And maybe roll the dough out if possible and cut circles out, those thicc bois look delicious but of you're trying to get closer to an oreo I think that would work better...


Okay I'm done 😂
